dct_title_s: A New and accurate map of New Jersey : from the best authorities
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Title within ornamental cartouche. From the Universal magazine, v. 66, June 1780. "W. long. from London." Historic Maps copy 1 has outline color.
